{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act16side", "eventName": "吾導先路", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "GA-1", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "燈下黑", "storyInfo": "塞茜莉亞的光環在見習執行者艾澤爾眼前閃爍、黯淡——然而如此年幼的薩科塔怎麼可能墮天？\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g3_laterano_cathedralballroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_263_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_262_1#2$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_263_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_262_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尤卡坦......你不覺得，拉特蘭的飲食有點問題嗎......？", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#2$1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_263_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_262_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相比謝拉格，這裡的口味確實有些偏甜了。", "name": "尤卡坦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_263_1#7$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_263_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_262_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，露絲你不是喜歡甜食嗎？", "name": "尤卡坦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_263_1#1$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_263_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_262_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那也不能所有的食物都是甜的吧！", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#8$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_263_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，我開始懷念謝拉格了。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都怪菈塔托絲那個臭女人，說什麼要抓住一切機會重新提高家族的地位......結果她自己又不來，把我丟到這麼遠的地方。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_263_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_262_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也是大夫人願意信任你的表現吧。畢竟在那件事之後的絕境裡，是靠著你和大夫人的共同努力，才確保了如今布朗陶家的地位。", "name": "尤卡坦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_263_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_263_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_262_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又把自己撇出去，尤卡坦，你該不會其實很享受隱居幕後的感覺吧？", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#10$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_263_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_262_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對我來說，能看到露絲散發光芒就已經很滿足了。", "name": "尤卡坦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_263_1#8$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_263_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_262_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......唔唔，你什麼時候學得這麼油嘴滑舌了！", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#4$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_263_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_262_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，夫人，這場會議或許確實比我們預想的更加有價值。", "name": "尤卡坦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_263_1#8$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來之前，我們甚至以為不會有多少國家回應邀請。現在看來，可能還是低估了拉特蘭的影響力。", "name": "尤卡坦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_263_1#8$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_263_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_262_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然你說得有道理......但是別想轉移話題！", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#3$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_262_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_175"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 50.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.9, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 50.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.3}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_175"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（萊塔尼亞語）哎呀，你長沒長眼睛！", "name": "刻薄的萊塔尼亞人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_262_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（萊塔尼亞語）是你撞上我的吧。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#4$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_262_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多麼蹩腳的萊塔尼亞語，哪裡來的鄉下人？", "name": "刻薄的萊塔尼亞人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我來自謝拉格，謝拉格可不是什麼鄉下。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝拉格？", "name": "刻薄的萊塔尼亞人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝拉格是什麼地方？", "name": "刻薄的萊塔尼亞人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_175", "name2": "avg_npc_360_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莎倫夫人，謝拉格是位於維多利亞、哥倫比亞、卡西米爾緩衝地帶的雪域國家。", "name": "開朗的萬國信使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_360_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_175"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那片雪山中還有國家？哈，那不就是鄉下嗎！", "name": "刻薄的萊塔尼亞人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "區區邊鄙小國的使者，也敢在本公爵夫人面前嘴硬？", "name": "刻薄的萊塔尼亞人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這位夫人，第一，我要再次強調，謝拉格並非你口中的“鄉下”。您不瞭解這個國家，可能是出於您的孤陋寡聞。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第二，撞上我的人是您，請您向我道歉。", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......！", "name": "刻薄的萊塔尼亞人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_175", "name2": "avg_npc_360_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莎倫夫人，這裡是大教堂......", "name": "開朗的萬國信使"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_360_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莎倫夫人，請容我提醒，您現在身在拉特蘭，而不是在您的萊塔尼亞領地。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你又是誰？", "name": "刻薄的萊塔尼亞人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉特蘭的萬國信使。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萬國信使，你是什麼意思？說什麼這裡是大教堂，怎麼，身為東道主，你想說拉特蘭會站在那個鄉下人一邊嗎？", "name": "刻薄的萊塔尼亞人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉特蘭站在規則一邊。所以，莎倫夫人，您應該向休露絲夫人道歉。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_262_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道我的名字？", "name": "休露絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_262_1#4$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "知道各國來使的名字是理所當然的事，不是嗎？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？這麼說，你很清楚我是誰。", "name": "刻薄的萊塔尼亞人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，萊塔尼亞的法蘭西斯公爵夫人。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但請容許我再次提醒您，這裡是拉特蘭，夫人。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在拉特蘭，請尊重戒律與規則。無論您在萊塔尼亞享有怎樣的特權，在拉特蘭，它們並不存在。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是拉特蘭的待客之道？", "name": "刻薄的萊塔尼亞人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果您願意做“拉特蘭的客人”，拉特蘭自然會竭誠以待。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#9$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_361_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——奧倫，你什麼時候開始代表拉特蘭了？", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#3$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_361_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "作為拉特蘭的使者，我沒有這個資格嗎？", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#3$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在大教堂，你沒有。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_361_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莎倫夫人，請息怒。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#5$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_175"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，樞機，現在想息事寧人，是不是有些晚了？", "name": "刻薄的萊塔尼亞人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_361_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "公爵夫人，我真誠地請求您的諒解。頂撞您的萬國信使會受到相應的處罰。晚些時候，您可以在下榻的賓館親眼確認教皇廳的誠意。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#5$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "休露絲夫人，也請求您的原諒，這一小小誤會是我們工作不周所致。如果您願意寬宏地接受我的歉意，我希望能邀請您稍後往偏廳一敘。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#5$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_262_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_263_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "休露絲看向尤卡坦，尤卡坦輕微地點了點頭。"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_175"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，拉特蘭人。罷了。", "name": "刻薄的萊塔尼亞人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_361_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿萊索，瑪蒂娜，請替我招待好三位貴賓。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#6$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧倫，隨我來。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_npc_361_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "處罰是吧，是，是......", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#10$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g7_laterano_ward", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，司提望區這名死者沒有留下遺囑和遺囑預登記資訊，稍晚我會回到公證所提交二次確認流程。", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在？我在司提望區中心醫院......不不，我沒事，是我遇到一個小姑娘摔傷了，正在帶她做檢查......", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#9$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我沒有交通肇事......", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#9$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，父母不在旁邊，她現在還在昏迷中，暫時無法確認家庭情況。等她醒來我會把她送回監護人身邊。", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，如果一時醒不來，也許我會需要使用公證所權限......", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......欸？可以把這作為實訓任務之一嗎？......好的，完成後我會補齊任務文書。", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......啊，不好意思，我聯絡完了。", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係！醫生查完體了，沒有發現外傷，頭部也沒有，應該不是因為撞到頭部而昏迷。", "name": "快嘴的醫院護工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過小姑娘有點低燒，可能本來就在生病。昏迷的具體原因還需要再做幾項檢查確認，但應該沒有大礙。", "name": "快嘴的醫院護工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "醫生把她安排在2127病房了，你可以在那邊等檢查結果。", "name": "快嘴的醫院護工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她是你妹妹嗎？你在執勤嗎？為什麼執行者執勤會帶著妹妹呀？我很少在司提望區碰到執行者呢！", "name": "快嘴的醫院護工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......她不是我妹妹。", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你為什麼送她來醫院？她是你的任務對象嗎？天哪，執行者真的這麼冷酷嗎？對這麼小的孩子執法？她做了什麼？", "name": "快嘴的醫院護工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我只是在路邊遇到了她，她不是我的任務對象，應該就是住在附近的孩子吧。", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#6$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎？那她應該是新搬過來的吧。", "name": "快嘴的醫院護工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "司提望區只有這一所醫院，附近的小孩子生病了都要來這裡看病......你真該看看換季時的兒科診室，太累人啦！", "name": "快嘴的醫院護工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好在我下周就要去療養部輪崗了。你知道我們院的療養部嗎？很有名哦！", "name": "快嘴的醫院護工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去年療養部的輪椅競速射擊賽冠軍，天哪，我從來沒有見過那麼快的銃，我懷疑那是一名銃騎閣下......雖然有點年輕。", "name": "快嘴的醫院護工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你那是什麼表情，我不是說了我們療養部很有名嗎？不止一位大教堂的人在我們這裡療養呢！", "name": "快嘴的醫院護工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你剛才是不是說，我送來醫院的小姑娘是新搬到司提望區的？", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為我從沒見過她嘛。既然不是你妹妹，這麼小的孩子，總不能是從別的區跑過來的吧？", "name": "快嘴的醫院護工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然啦，也可能就是湊巧我沒見過她。但這個小姑娘一看就是三天兩頭生病的類型......我可見得太多啦！", "name": "快嘴的醫院護工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛才是不是說到兒科診室？上周......", "name": "快嘴的醫院護工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃莉莎，你又在和家屬聊天了。醫生讓你去檢查中心取結果。", "name": "嚴肅的護士"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好——", "name": "快嘴的醫院護工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#4$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你確定取對了報告？", "name": "認真的醫生"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，有什麼問題嗎？", "name": "快嘴的醫院護工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_368_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從來沒見過這麼奇怪的血樣分析。", "name": "認真的醫生"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......複印好了，你幫我把原件送去院長室。帶上我寫的條子。", "name": "認真的醫生"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要去一趟療養部。", "name": "認真的醫生"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g10_laterano_roof", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_365_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嘖，那個護工去的方向是院長室。帕蒂亞，該怎麼辦？", "name": "拉特蘭市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_365_1#1$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_357_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......分兩個人去攔住送報告的人。別鬧大，只要拖延一下，爭取到一些時間就行。", "name": "帕蒂亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_357_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個醫生呢？", "name": "帕蒂亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_357_1#1$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_365_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他去的好像是療養部。倒是沒有去塞茜莉亞那邊。", "name": "拉特蘭市民？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_365_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_357_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？也好。這樣那個執行者暫時還不會知道。", "name": "帕蒂亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_357_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其他人跟我一起，引開執行者，趁醫院的人過來之前帶走塞茜莉亞。", "name": "帕蒂亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_357_1#1$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記住，要快，但是不要對塞茜莉亞動粗。", "name": "帕蒂亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_357_1#1$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她是我們的同伴。", "name": "帕蒂亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_357_1#1$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別讓她討厭我們。", "name": "帕蒂亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_357_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$distressed_intro", "key": "$distressed_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "媽媽，為什麼每次去見爸爸都要走這麼遠呀？天好黑......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "因為......爸爸沒辦法來拉特蘭城，不能和我們住在一起。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "為什麼呀？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "因為他和我們不一樣。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "那我們不能和爸爸在一起嗎？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "......爸爸不會希望塞茜莉亞和他一起，你以後會明白......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "為什麼......爸爸不喜歡我嗎？是不是我做得不夠好？\\n如果我做個好孩子，爸爸可以一直在我們身邊嗎？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "......塞茜莉亞，你要相信爸爸，他愛你，即使他不在我們身邊。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "26_i01", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔......嗯......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "媽媽......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你醒了！", "name": "艾澤爾"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是......這是哪裡......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡是醫院，小妹妹。你在大街上昏倒了，我沒有找到你的爸爸媽媽，就帶你來了醫院。", "name": "艾澤爾"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "醫院......這裡就是醫院嗎？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不對......你，你穿著制服，媽媽說......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的媽媽，對你說了什麼嗎？", "name": "艾澤爾"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（說起來，剛見到我時，她是不是躲開我了......？）", "name": "艾澤爾"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，小妹妹，我可以帶你去找媽媽。我不是壞人。", "name": "艾澤爾"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以幫我找媽媽嗎？媽媽，媽媽被穿著袍子的人帶走了！", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（......難道這是一樁綁架案！所以她才會一個人留在那裡？）", "name": "艾澤爾"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小妹妹，別著急，我是公證所的執行者，我會幫你找媽媽的。你媽媽是怎麼被人帶走的？", "name": "艾澤爾"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你是公證所的......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，我是公證所的，我叫艾澤爾，你看，這是我的工牌。", "name": "艾澤爾"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你真的會幫我找媽媽？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然了。你叫什麼名字？", "name": "艾澤爾"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我是塞茜莉亞。", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......唔......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "afrom": 0.0, "rfrom": 0.0, "gfrom": 0.0, "bfrom": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$flashback", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "afrom": 0.0, "rfrom": 0.0, "gfrom": 0.0, "bfrom": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$flashback", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "26_i15", "screenadapt": "showall", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "？！光環......怎麼會......", "name": "艾澤爾"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（這是怎麼回事......薩科塔即使在情緒最低落的時候，光環也不會如此黯淡。）", "name": "艾澤爾"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（除非......）", "name": "艾澤爾"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（......可是這麼小的孩子，大概連守護銃都還沒拿到，怎麼可能......？）", "name": "艾澤爾"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嗯......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（不，比起這些......）", "name": "艾澤爾"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塞茜莉亞，你很難受嗎？你的光環......？", "name": "艾澤爾"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......有時候......會這樣......媽媽說是生病了......一會兒就好了......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "艾澤爾"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾澤爾發現了一件事。"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塞茜莉亞此時正在痛苦之中，也因為找不到母親而焦急。"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他沒有感受到從塞茜莉亞那裡傳達而來的痛苦和焦急。"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塞茜莉亞......無疑是薩科塔。"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這怎麼可能？"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g7_laterano_ward", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塞茜莉亞，你......", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "PlaySound", "attrib